snippet.title: Lorry Hill
snippet.description:
My name is Lorry Hill and as long as I can remember I have been absolutely entranced by what makes a person physically beautiful.  I have spent most of my life entrenched in the world of beauty, makeup and most of all plastic surgery and cosmetic procedures.  I have unique access to the world of plastic surgeons (and who really is the best of the best for most every facial procedure) through a private network of friends and associates who share their wisdom and knowledge with me.
    Although I am not a doctor; I have an extremely well informed opinion garnered from my own plastic surgeries coupled with a talent for discerning what facial feature combinations are objectively beautiful.  
     My goal for this channel is to inform you of the best plastic surgery procedures with the best results as well as caution you about the plastic surgeries and cosmetic procedures that should be avoided. I also plan to explore the world of skincare and discern the best products for anti-aging.
